## Triple Whale Pricing at a Glance

Triple Whale uses GMV-based pricing — your cost is determined by your trailing 12-month gross merchandise value. The published "starting from" prices are misleading because they only apply to the smallest GMV brackets.

### Plan Overview

| Plan | Base Price (Annual) | What's Added |
|------|-------------------|-------------|
| **Founders Dashboard** | Free | Basic dashboard, limited lookback |
| **Growth** | From $129/mo | Triple Pixel, anomaly detection, standard analytics |
| **Pro** | From $199/mo | AI recommendations (Moby), RFM audiences, email/SMS attribution |
| **Enterprise** | From $279/mo | Creative insights, product analytics, dedicated CSM |

### The Real Cost: GMV Brackets

Those base prices only apply to the smallest GMV brackets. Here's what brands actually pay:

| Annual GMV | Approximate Monthly Cost |
|------------|--------------------------|
| Up to $500K | Free (Founders Dash) or ~$129/mo (Growth) |
| $500K-$1M | ~$249-$349/mo |
| $1M-$2.5M | ~$549/mo |
| $2.5M-$5M | ~$749-$899/mo |
| $5M-$7M | ~$1,129/mo |
| $7M-$10M | ~$1,500-$2,000/mo |
| $10M-$25M | ~$2,000-$3,500/mo |
| $25M+ | ~$3,500-$4,489+/mo |
| $50M+ | Custom enterprise pricing |

Annual billing is cheaper than monthly. Annual subscriptions are approximately $2,990-$3,990/year for lower GMV brackets.

