## Hidden Costs

### 1. Month-to-Month Premium

Displayed prices are for annual billing. Monthly billing costs approximately 17%+ more. If you want flexibility, you'll pay for it.

### 2. Shopify Lock-In

Triple Whale is built for Shopify. Non-Shopify e-commerce platforms get reduced functionality. If you're on WooCommerce, BigCommerce, Magento, or a custom platform, many features won't work or will work partially.

### 3. Free Tier Limitations

The Founders Dashboard is useful for evaluation but has limited data lookback and no Triple Pixel. You'll outgrow it quickly once you start running paid ads.

### 4. One Good Quarter = Higher Bracket

GMV is measured on trailing 12 months. A single strong quarter can push you into a higher pricing bracket. Once there, you stay at the higher price even if the next quarter is slower.

