## Bottom Line

Triple Whale is a strong Shopify-first analytics platform with good AI recommendations and a comprehensive feature set. The GMV scaling trap is the main concern — at higher revenue levels ($5M+), the same features cost 2-6x more than at lower levels.

If you're a sub-$2M Shopify brand, Triple Whale Pro is reasonably priced and full-featured. If you're growing past $5M GMV and watching costs climb, alternatives like Northbeam and mbuzz offer attribution without revenue-based scaling.

